reviews.text:
This restaurant is Not Hygienic in sorounding. A lot of bad smell and flies are all over the dining tables 
Food lovers are really disturbing and will make runway without eating their order 
Suggested to move the rubbish dumping spot where gov dumping area is just 50 metres away

Simple but delicious food. I eat here once a week.
